      <title>Clover Press: The Art of Storytelling</title>
      <author>Clover Press</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//books/clover-press-art-storytelling-books</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">93936085d255e4de9175a0c5a6749578d2035a89</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Jun 2025 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/1615116f7cb7857c13a3118024625bea402635f7.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=eec2de583f0c11411db686d2d6e91083"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/62953dc4abf362e99634a3d4b52523d769fd2174.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=42cc765c661160ab3236bdb08411fa46"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Curated comics + more by Clover Press&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’ve partnered with Clover Press to deliver members a lesson in the art of storytelling. Lose yourself in outstanding graphic novels and ebooks rich with narrative depth and striking visuals. Follow the mystery of Jay Gatsby in a vivid reimagining of the Roaring Twenties in &lt;em&gt;The Great Gatsby&lt;/em&gt;, experience a modern retelling of an ancient classic in &lt;em&gt;Dracula of Transylvania&lt;/em&gt;, and explore a cautionary tale of corporate greed in &lt;em&gt;BILLI 99&lt;/em&gt;. Plus, your purchase helps support The Hero Initiative.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#grievling"&gt;GRIEVLING&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#kabumpoinoz"&gt;KABUMPO IN OZ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#votingisyoursuperpower"&gt;VOTING IS YOUR SUPERPOWER!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#diablohouseshortstorycollection"&gt;DIABLO HOUSE SHORT STORY COLLECTION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#greatgatsbyillustratednovel"&gt;GREAT GATSBY ILLUSTRATED NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#pirates_atreasureofcomicstoplunderarrr"&gt;PIRATES: A TREASURE OF COMICS TO PLUNDER ,ARRR!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#tragedieofmacbethgraphicnovel"&gt;TRAGEDIE OF MACBETH GRAPHIC NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#billi99"&gt;BILLI 99&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#draculaoftransylvania"&gt;DRACULA OF TRANSYLVANIA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#greatgatsbygraphicnovel"&gt;GREAT GATSBY GRAPHIC NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#kevineastmanstotallytwistedtales"&gt;KEVIN EASTMAN'S TOTALLY TWISTED TALES&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#possessed"&gt;POSSESSED&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#artofdraculaoftransylvania"&gt;ART OF DRACULA OF TRANSYLVANIA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#armoreds1to5"&gt;ARMORED #'s 1 to 5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#continentalop"&gt;CONTINENTAL OP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#petevonshollyslovecraftillustrated"&gt;PETE VON SHOLLY'S LOVECRAFT ILLUSTRATED&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#diablohousegraphicnovel"&gt;DIABLO HOUSE GRAPHIC NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#golemofvenicebeach"&gt;GOLEM OF VENICE BEACH&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#petevonshollyshistoryofmonsters"&gt;PETE VON SHOLLY'S HISTORY OF MONSTERS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#projectmk-ultra_thecompletecollection"&gt;PROJECT MK-ULTRA: THE COMPLETE COLLECTION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#royalbookofoz"&gt;ROYAL BOOK OF OZ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="grievling"&gt;&lt;a id="grievling" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/grievling_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=0eefb1e1797d3f3ef314338c9ed57d04d6a66876dd43c13fd811857b4823bafb"&gt;GRIEVLING&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ac43419cbc0012462efa116280ff82576fa0f3b9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3a94771ece9ca9548a7ca4da01d467c6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set in a small town in middle America, The Grievling is a tale of death and revenge featuring a young girl who returns from the grave after a bullying incident taken too far leads to her accidental murder.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="kabumpoinoz"&gt;&lt;a id="kabumpoinoz" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/kabumpoinoz_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=7912ccd6400a119bb5d5998dd368075acef7668ee875be3e2eadfc18db3069fe"&gt;KABUMPO IN OZ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c7e9822cb79287409f109d110b36ab42ebf83e07.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=971a5f038c5cc5201f135c464645762a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kabumpo in Oz is the 16th book in the Oz series. It is also the second book in the series written by Ruth Plumly Thompson. This new edition features a new cover and interior illustrations by Eisner nominated artist Sara Richard.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="votingisyoursuperpower"&gt;&lt;a id="votingisyoursuperpower" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/votingisyoursuperpower_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=c9c810953c0e589e59325f8e6555df500d94b5633df295df39c391a4883d853a"&gt;VOTING IS YOUR SUPERPOWER!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/e0f604650546fd3237140565605140a39bce0eea.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=862f6fa484e57475c9b9d2b87bda9534"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this 104 page book of comics, you will find a timeless and compelling message of inspiration, motivation, and duty to exercise your right to cast your vote. And when you finish and put down this book you will not only have been entertained and enlightened, but you will have realized voting IS your superpower, more formidable than a bat-a-rang, x-ray vision, spider-sense, and a magic-lasso assembled together!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="diablohouseshortstorycollection"&gt;&lt;a id="diablohouseshortstorycollection" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/diablohouseshortstorycollection_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=5d6bcd2ecc2a287b6574c073bb28f5c769dea289d1e8f469755ee4c4192c495c"&gt;DIABLO HOUSE SHORT STORY COLLECTION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c1348b39e08431e0c1161e64e78469fc4a2aac8d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=14270ec8c3ac72a276724219a4b9e2c3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of seven horror prose stories that take place in Diablo House. Also includes Grady's Hendrix's comics debut with art by Damien Worm.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="greatgatsbyillustratednovel"&gt;&lt;a id="greatgatsbyillustratednovel" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/greatgatsbyillustratednovel_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=cdf4efb13ef081b5f11902ea73d6eee4044d33454f6e8e753327d1df52fd55f6"&gt;GREAT GATSBY ILLUSTRATED NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9277aa08c81608ed09b643a17594c1a638ff9921.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d55c4b00b25552b09310b82cf3d358db"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step back into the Roaring Twenties with F. Scott Fitzgerald's timeless masterpiece, The Great Gatsby, now re-imagined as a stunning illustrated edition. Featuring gorgeous illustrations by Jorge Coelho.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="pirates_atreasureofcomicstoplunderarrr"&gt;&lt;a id="pirates_atreasureofcomicstoplunderarrr" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/pirates_atreasureofcomicstoplunderarrr_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=087926f050a2c49c5c800c7613ec645e6f54323e6d94120a97e58663dd6d7fd6"&gt;PIRATES: A TREASURE OF COMICS TO PLUNDER ,ARRR!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/bee29daf35183a83bf82093b98dffff37ecb9153.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b0c096452e236d5bbfb2c6dfa730317d"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Swashbuckling artists the likes of Frank Frazetta, Reed Crandall, Graham Ingels, Dick Briefer, etc. give ya complete comics stories to plunder, arrr!  Plus feast on art by bilge rats Wally Wood, Bernard Krigstein, Carl Burgos, Howard Pyle, and, yarrr, more!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="tragedieofmacbethgraphicnovel"&gt;&lt;a id="tragedieofmacbethgraphicnovel" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/tragedieofmacbethgraphicnovel_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=652fad1d7acfb5186527da0eb1ced0e4a2dc2a0fba1eabf730f12d465d486396"&gt;TRAGEDIE OF MACBETH GRAPHIC NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fa11273072d0c84cb693a4cd81011a2db84bd59f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ea882244c2e5918735ef09eef44c5d76"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shakespeare died over 400 years ago and no story captures the mysticism and brutality of Scottish history quite like 'Macbeth'. This graphic novel aims to tell the darkest version yet of this tale of witchcraft, murder, manipulation, and unbridled ambition... Also includes the original play-script by Shakespeare.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="billi99"&gt;&lt;a id="billi99" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/billi99_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=ae89a7efc276fdb0819251b1950c721dedbeae2e8d87cf2ac9b56803150dbce5"&gt;BILLI 99&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4ea5f6a5a5255c8f0ffa2f31e3e93e7d1c52b883.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9ed586e12ef00df7ab80dd3d84d5a0cd"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set in 1999, Billi 99 embodies a cautionary tale in which corporate greed and corrupt government affected an America very much like our own today. With that, they posed the question, what is power when everything has been taken away?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="draculaoftransylvania"&gt;&lt;a id="draculaoftransylvania" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/draculaoftransylvania_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=ca7f703a89399136d71a20bb9bd7a8a4540bb61e5bcfb7c2012a6d953e1c1af2"&gt;DRACULA OF TRANSYLVANIA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/501c8c1c207ff3a4ce6b382b1cd7779728c037a3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=1f1511bb85fdd2eb169a0972e45d5d65"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Young Solicitor Jonathan Harker braves ghosts, demons, living skeletons, and armies of rats—all of which pale in comparison to his encounters with Dracula of Transylvania, the Son of Satan. The demonic, shapeshifting vampire imposes his wrath, malice and vengeance upon an England about to enter the Modern Era.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="greatgatsbygraphicnovel"&gt;&lt;a id="greatgatsbygraphicnovel" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/greatgatsbygraphicnovel_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=5d01039617313228a1ab405567d487a8ed93e6a97ded72e4dbfc8e65ed7697e4"&gt;GREAT GATSBY GRAPHIC NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a1751c5ac7c5741859f78fe80d6ca1309d4c19dd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f26a3633b17769578144db187c9e6de9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you already love the book or are experiencing it for the first time, we’ve got you covered. It’s all here, the roaring ‘20s in all its glory --the decadent parties, the gangsters, the car crashes, the love triangle, and so much more. Young and old can appreciate the dedication of veteran comic creators, Adams and Coelho, as they adapt this American classic story into the classic American art form of comics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="kevineastmanstotallytwistedtales"&gt;&lt;a id="kevineastmanstotallytwistedtales" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/kevineastmanstotallytwistedtales_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=9242f1847cc1c389d322f9e68d67b7a1225dc0be7edb2a4d5bd367c8784d0ff8"&gt;KEVIN EASTMAN'S TOTALLY TWISTED TALES&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/56cc8152c620b65a367ab272b8d4444c830d5015.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=b8d0d0256f96234b0116c6757889dcb5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kevin Eastman’s Totally Twisted Tales is 96 pages of dark and twisted depravity from the clinically insane minds of Kevin Eastman and Simon Bisley! Includes three full length stories featuring guys, girls, monsters, mutants, superheroes, slackers and lowlifes – as well as one VERY fast rat!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="possessed"&gt;&lt;a id="possessed" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/possessed_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=a6874f28bcf7a3b488f11650fd5204ee9adff866b3e477c55552f871724ae010"&gt;POSSESSED&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/abbb61c70bde21dcb6fbc361547da612540a41fc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=acd185ed2301a62803280fc2f457e183"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In Nazi-occupied Budapest, a young woman sees her mother and father brutally murdered by an SS Officer. She escapes with her Grandfather and the help of a Rabbi. Filled with rage and hatred, the Grandfather asks the Rabbi for help and he shows them an ancient box that contains a demon filled with hate and violence. They can have the revenge they want but only by giving up their sense of right and wrong.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="artofdraculaoftransylvania"&gt;&lt;a id="artofdraculaoftransylvania" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/artofdraculaoftransylvania_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=e79e8e89f2a5d992643df3d6c4309f6985180bdfa37d4de20c4933fb98075856"&gt;ART OF DRACULA OF TRANSYLVANIA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/96437821b3cd44354869923902102faa2628bf56.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a09d158e4751f953d12fdc8146c4d552"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A collection of exotic locations, designs, and concepts behind Dracula of Translyvania featuring never-before-seen art from Delgado's world of vampires.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="armoreds1to5"&gt;&lt;a id="armoreds1to5" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/armoreds1to5_preview_v2.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=7db4f7057b598c7330d6044d9f9885a3780e6d8b64b70c79046568670d70ae71"&gt;ARMORED #'s 1 to 5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/0dabec19d4b00942b06013672e375e932a3fe8b0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=93cc2a73bfade6d3a2987eec2c6e666c"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Andy's just been adopted by a quaint family living in the countryside. He stumbles across a mystical suit of armo haunted by the ghost who wore it centuries ago. What could go wrong?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="continentalop"&gt;&lt;a id="continentalop" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/continentalop_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=80bebf04ebb3e75cf779d3e45377f74800187d96b0d731c65047c2c2d7cab4e3"&gt;CONTINENTAL OP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/91e1fef25028408a014289a42ffa92fc6eaea557.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3ad1dae6a39ebd120cf47d13b9bedab3"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a collection of the first five stories in Hammett’s series of shorts, including Arson Plus, Crooked Souls, Slippery Fingers, It, and Bodies Piled Up; all lavishly illustrated by John K. Snyder III.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="petevonshollyslovecraftillustrated"&gt;&lt;a id="petevonshollyslovecraftillustrated" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/petevonshollyslovecraftillustrated_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=8bb01830f529a79c620cae9c825015104158f50f4ed3fee3e18054bc063357b4"&gt;PETE VON SHOLLY'S LOVECRAFT ILLUSTRATED&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d3dc43693f9d6df994dda6b7ff3c7a3134a28f6d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=46565e5cc4ead21e8f9ff504357a8404"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A full color collection of over 325 images covering ALL the fiction of H.P. Lovecraft arranged in the order in which the stories were written. The book also features notes. sketches and an intro by S. T. Joshi.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="diablohousegraphicnovel"&gt;&lt;a id="diablohousegraphicnovel" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/diablohousegraphicnovel_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=d7832d24bb68659fa4e5ee018e349aa01e1958c663c331111663ab344a712c07"&gt;DIABLO HOUSE GRAPHIC NOVEL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/031d48fcd1b1a440449bb87bbcf3f4daab09fa30.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=66e6b7f8702458657e5ce0b2594bb5c4"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In La Jolla, California stands Diablo House. It'll make your dreams come true, if you dare. Surf-bum and host, Riley, invites us into his home and shares stories of the people who let their desires come at the cost of all else.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="golemofvenicebeach"&gt;&lt;a id="golemofvenicebeach" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/golemofvenicebeach_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=91fbac9f7acb6e1b8ead45141f4cd3c26968234e8790f27a5cbf7708cea32a60"&gt;GOLEM OF VENICE BEACH&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c84c392fc00631088c930adf88e8674816a0b6d1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=87bad23c0244da6627e4e95290555e41"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This 152-page graphic novel about the adventures of a 400-year-old Golem spans from 16th century Europe to the horrors of World War II to modern day Venice Beach, where the Golem becomes entangled in a war between a gang and the police.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="petevonshollyshistoryofmonsters"&gt;&lt;a id="petevonshollyshistoryofmonsters" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/petevonshollyshistoryofmonsters_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=1770930edc472ef1a6de79ca610101226c5fe3b71bc07d896ad8fb91af775ba8"&gt;PETE VON SHOLLY'S HISTORY OF MONSTERS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2968172915e1b5527bf915494b79f119bcb27dd3.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=dadec3fbadf69b35f729c94009e37100"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This unprecedented illustrated pageant shows the actual history of monsters from man's earliest fears of the darkness beyond the fire to today's nightmares to see how these terrors found expression in myth, legend, and entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="projectmk-ultra_thecompletecollection"&gt;&lt;a id="projectmk-ultra_thecompletecollection" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/projectmk-ultra_thecompletecollection_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=08c8c311ba012638be15f8920749892a8a8c8b04630ee8f15b4d68af3df1854b"&gt;PROJECT MK-ULTRA: THE COMPLETE COLLECTION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6d258b09d8f3922032b70cc367b8617e060171dd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ef2d3fc73d4aae1ef6ee350d8228b8df"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This original graphic novel brings to life the harrowing story of the CIA's mind control program, which used drugs, hypnosis, and other methods to manipulate the behavior of unwitting subjects. With careful attention to historical facts and rampant conspiracy theories, Stewart Kenneth Moore, Scott Sampila, and Brandon Beckner have crafted a gripping narrative that takes readers deep inside the shadowy world of government conspiracies and covert operations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="royalbookofoz"&gt;&lt;a id="royalbookofoz" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/royalbookofoz_preview.pdf?t=st=1752337177~exp=1752423577~hmac=ba52e065e369893b6a92cca665f39b159b5bc9c9a22fdace63c5ed3931a0600b"&gt;ROYAL BOOK OF OZ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c121751a538977614abf39aafa5f8a69a42d2522.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=25cde764c5bcbe07f44ccdb4ca3b46af"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Royal Book of Oz is the 15th book in the Oz series. It is also the first book in the series written by Ruth Plumly Thompson.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
