g for Stocks Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#promptengineeringartandscience-buildllm-basedappsinpython"&gt;Prompt Engineering Art and Science - Build LLM-Based Apps in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#thecompleteappdevelopmentwithgpt-4inpythonmasterclass"&gt;The Complete App Development with GPT-4 in Python Masterclass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#best-sellingmicrosoftcopilotinexcel-promptengineeringtoolkit"&gt;Best-Selling Microsoft CoPilot in Excel - Prompt Engineering Toolkit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#promptengineeringperfectionplaybookforgenerativeaiwithpython"&gt;Prompt Engineering Perfection Playbook for Generative AI with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#5plushourgenaiappdevelopmentwithgooglegeminiinpythonunreal5godotandunity"&gt;5+ HOUR GenAI App Development with Google Gemini in Python, Unreal 5, Godot &amp; Unity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildcomputervisionprojectswithneuralnetworkstesseractandopencvinpython"&gt;Build Computer Vision Projects with Neural Networks, Tesseract and OpenCV in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#naturallanguageprocessingmachinelearningbootcampwithpython"&gt;Natural Language Processing Machine Learning Bootcamp with Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#algorithmictradingwithnaturallanguageprocessingandmachinelearninginpython"&gt;Algorithmic Trading with Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#theessentialcopilotpromptengineeringcookbook"&gt;The Essential Copilot Prompt Engineering Cookbook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#1rankedpythonmachinelearning6plushourbundlewithcursor-masterai-poweredcoding"&gt;#1 Ranked Python Machine Learning 6+ HOUR Bundle with Cursor - Master AI-Powered Coding&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildviralgenerativeaiappswithgptinpython"&gt;Build Viral Generative AI Apps with GPT in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#1googlegeminichatbotpromptengineering4plushourbundle"&gt;#1 Google Gemini Chatbot Prompt Engineering 4+ HOUR Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#essentialanthropicpromptengineeringmastery5plushourbundle"&gt;Essential Anthropic Prompt Engineering Mastery 5+ HOUR Bundle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#financemachinelearning3plushourbundlewithpythonandcursorai"&gt;Finance Machine Learning 3+ HOUR Bundle with Python and Cursor AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#designllmapps-acompleteapproachinpython"&gt;Design LLM Apps - A Complete Approach in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildrecommendationalgorithms-machinelearningtotriggerclicksinpython"&gt;Build Recommendation Algorithms - Machine Learning to Trigger Clicks in Python&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="dataengineerportfolioreadiness-pythonandpandasexplorationandmanipulationprojects"&gt;&lt;a id="dataengineerportfolioreadiness-pythonandpandasexplorationandmanipulationprojects"&gt;Data Engineer Portfolio Readiness - Python and Pandas Exploration and Manipulation Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2ee6fbcbe013a453b84e36b3dabf13ac14d4c650.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=bd9408c426398ceb374155d4c267a042"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to land your next role in data engineering? This hands-on course helps you build a job-ready portfolio by mastering Python and Pandas—the essential toolkit for every modern data engineer.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;✅ Work with real-world datasets to perform in-depth data exploration and cleaning&lt;br&gt;✅ Use Pandas for filtering, grouping, reshaping, merging, and advanced transformation tasks&lt;br&gt;✅ Visualize and summarize large datasets to prepare for pipelines and modeling&lt;br&gt;✅ Handle missing values, detect outliers, and prepare production-grade data structures&lt;br&gt;✅ Showcase your skills with end-to-end projects that simulate professional data engineering tasks&lt;br&gt;✅ Learn best practices for clean code, readable notebooks, and scalable data solutions&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Build your portfolio as you learn—every project is designed to be resume- and interview-ready.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Includes downloadable Jupyter notebooks, datasets, code templates, and lifetime access—available now only in this exclusive Humble Bundle launch.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;If you're aiming for a career in data engineering or want to sharpen your data manipulation skills, this is your launchpad. Enroll now and start building a portfolio that gets noticed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="hands-ondatascienceandmachinelearningportfoliodevelopmentwithpythonandscikit-learn"&gt;&lt;a id="hands-ondatascienceandmachinelearningportfoliodevelopmentwithpythonandscikit-learn"&gt;Hands-On Data Science and Machine Learning Portfolio Development with Python and Scikit-Learn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/06aaa8512ec46c3f556f7cfbd7b1841f424688f2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=20ac03d0691baa58a396a58e8c960c48"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ready to break into data science and machine learning—even with zero prior experience? This hands-on bootcamp is the perfect starting point. You’ll learn core concepts by building a real project: performing sentiment analysis using unsupervised classification, powered by the most important Python tools in the industry.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;✅ Learn the fundamentals of Python for data science—no experience needed&lt;br&gt;✅ Work with real-world text data to explore, clean, and prepare datasets &lt;br&gt;✅ Use Pandas and NumPy for efficient data manipulation and transformation&lt;br&gt;✅ Visualize insights with Matplotlib to tell powerful data stories &lt;br&gt;✅ Perform sentiment analysis using unsupervised learning techniques &lt;br&gt;✅ Apply clustering algorithms with Scikit-Learn to group and classify data without labeled examples &lt;br&gt;✅ Understand the core logic behind machine learning workflows, from preprocessing to model interpretation&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Build confidence with hands-on coding challenges and a complete beginner project you can showcase.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Includes starter datasets, sample code, project files, and lifetime access with updates.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;If you're ready to launch your journey into machine learning and data science, this course gives you the tools—and the confidence—to start strong. Enroll now and build your first intelligent project in Python.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt15"&gt;Pay $15 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="facedetectionandimageunderstandingwithpythonandopencv"&gt;&lt;a id="facedetectionandimageunderstandingwithpythonandopencv"&gt;Face Detection and Image Understanding with Python and OpenCV&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/49e799a8f288ecf23192521baea34db7fefdc631.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=040d825c6a772be75adab381b93a0227"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of computer vision by learning how to detect faces, understand images, and process visual data using Python and OpenCV. This hands-on course is perfect for developers, AI enthusiasts, and computer vision beginners looking to build real-world skills.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;✅ Detect faces in images and video streams with precision using Haar cascades and deep learning models&lt;br&gt;✅ Understand how image processing works—explore color spaces, contours, edges, and regions of interest&lt;br&gt;✅ Apply masking, thresholding, and object segmentation for advanced image analysis&lt;br&gt;✅ Build intelligent systems that extract features, track motion, and recognize facial landmarks&lt;br&gt;✅ Perform real-time face detection in video with Python and OpenCV&lt;br&gt;✅ Use image filters, transformations, and noise reduction techniques to enhance image quality&lt;br&gt