que Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 122&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 242&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , UE5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="modernartmuseumenvironmentartmuseumexhibitionshowroom"&gt;&lt;a id="modernartmuseumenvironmentartmuseumexhibitionshowroom" href="https://youtu.be/6bSMiheUHQc"&gt;Modern Art Museum Environment ( Art Museum Exhibition Showroom )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Showroom / Museum / Exhibition Hall includes 25 Unique Original Paintings / Drawings all made by me ( Nurten Babaoglu ), there is a Material instance that gives opportunity to change pictures with one click, includes 82 Unique Meshes and 25 Paintings / Drawings, Good for Games and Virtual Production Works,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;25 Unique Paintings / Drawings&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy Switch between Paintings.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sculptures&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Construction Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 82&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 98&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Textures: 167&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1K , 2K textures&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Supported Versions : 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , UE5 , 5.1 , 5.2 , 5.3 , 5.4+&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="modernhomeandhouseinteriorwith22originalmodernpaintingspainting"&gt;&lt;a id="modernhomeandhouseinteriorwith22originalmodernpaintingspainting"&gt;Modern Home / House Interior with 22 Original Modern Paintings ( Painting )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/35d530b073b4896a9431a1d11ce22ec4b2ce4890.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a0f9f4b83653d250e51d4d36