s made to look real and be easy to use. Whether it’s for a cinematic scene, an open-world game, or a slice-of-life project, this area is ready to go.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here’s what I packed for you:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Modular entertainment area structure (walls, doors, floors, ceiling lights)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Arcade machines, pool table, air hockey, pinball units&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Snack bar props: vending machines, popcorn stands, soda dispensers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Neon signs, seating, wall art, clutter props&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Interior and exterior areas with lively colors, signs of use, and cozy lighting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;PBR textures with 2K &amp;amp; 4K resolution (Albedo, Normal, Roughness, AO, Metallic)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanite-compatible meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom collisions for gameplay-ready, Optimized for both interior and exterior lighting setups&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material instances for easy color tweaks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;179 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Meshes: 179 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 149&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Number of Textures: 252&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5, 5.6+&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="tirerepairshop"&gt;&lt;a id="tirerepairshop" href="https://youtu.be/yxzRckeyLZg"&gt;Tire Repair Shop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hey there, developer buddy! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From grease-stained floors to stacked tires and heavy-duty equipment, every asset is crafted and textured for realism. Whether you’re building an industrial district, a roadside stop, or a cinematic environment, this pack has you covered.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here’s what I packed for you:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Modular shop interior (garage doors, walls, floors, service bays)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Tire stacks, rims, repair tools, compressors, jacks, balancers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Weathered exterior with signage, awning, and realistic wear&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Clutter props: oil cans, toolboxes, pallets, rags, debris&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Street props: trash bins, cones, parking lines&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;HEY BUDDY, HERE'S A DISCLAIMER:Enable the HDRI Plugin for the best lighting and reflections!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Key Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✨ PBR textures (2K &amp;amp; 4K: Albedo, Normal, Roughness, AO, Metallic)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✨ Nanite-compatible meshes for next-gen performance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✨ Custom collisions — gameplay-ready out of the box&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✨ Optimized for both interior and exterior scenes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✨ Material instances for easy color, dirt, and wear tweaks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;100 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game r