      <title>Becoming a C++ and Unreal Game Developer by Packt</title>
      <author>Packt</author>
      <link>https://humblebundle.com//software/becoming-c-and-unreal-game-developer-packt-software</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">05be3cc7990e13e913ef5d74cfe7add218d5f520</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Jun 2025 18:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5d2009b862f906ebe572a9e4eeb1450b291b37b3.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=961a5e2419d22671348cbc6f0868cf99"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/734c050f60c56ddc2c9a177c3136797e0e964f16.png?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=1c804ad4a7ab6bf22188247d5fd0f1f6"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Unreal tools for game devs&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to create video games in Unreal Engine and C++ from the pros at Packt with our latest Humble Video Learning Bundle. Master modern game development with comprehensive courses designed to help you succeed quickly—like &lt;em&gt;Creating Stunning Environments in Unreal Engine 5 – A Game Artist Bootcamp&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Complete Modern C++&lt;/em&gt;. Get the expert education you seek from the professionals at Packt, and help support Alzheimer's Research UK with your purchase!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealengine_ultimatesurvivalhorrorcourse"&gt;Unreal Engine - Ultimate Survival Horror Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealengine5_endlessrunner"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 - Endless Runner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completecplusplusdevelopercourse"&gt;The Complete C++ Developer Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#substancepaintertounrealengine5masterclass"&gt;Substance Painter to Unreal Engine 5 Masterclass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealengine5beginnersguidetobuildinga3denvironment"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 Beginner's Guide to Building a 3D Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#practicalcplusplus_learncplusplusbasicsstepbystep"&gt;Practical C++: Learn C++ Basics Step by Step&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cpluspluscrashcourse_quickandpracticallearning"&gt;C++ Crash Course - Quick and Practical Learning&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fundamentalsofobject-orientedprogramming_cplusplus"&gt;Fundamentals of Object-Oriented Programming - C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#buildingmedievalworlds_unrealengine5modularkitbash"&gt;Building Medieval Worlds - Unreal Engine 5 Modular Kitbash&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#creatingstunningenvironmentsinunrealengine5_agameartistbootcamp"&gt;Creating Stunning Environments in Unreal Engine 5 - A Game Artist Bootcamp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#completemoderncpluspluscplusplus11and14and17"&gt;Complete Modern C++ (C++11/14/17)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#behavioraldesignpatternsincplusplus"&gt;Behavioral Design Patterns in C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealengine5_thecompletebeginnerscourse"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 - The Complete Beginner's Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealengine5_theintermediatecourse"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 - The Intermediate Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unrealengine5forgames_physics"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 for Games - Physics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#structuraldesignpatternsinmoderncplusplus"&gt;Structural Design Patterns in Modern C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cplusplus20mastery_pureandunfiltered"&gt;C++ 20 Mastery - Pure and Unfiltered&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealengine_ultimatesurvivalhorrorcourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealengine_ultimatesurvivalhorrorcourse" href="https://youtu.be/TW9E3lPHCH4"&gt;Unreal Engine - Ultimate Survival Horror Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3afb8ac702d5b8a464daf31cdf715941038f1f43.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6a1a994071ecbd0bcfa42c4104bb4b99"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course will teach you how to make a survival horror game, teaching all skillsets and fundamentals of game creation through one of the most popular genres of in-game media. We will go step by step through the game-making process to show how we can set up a character from scratch, well-designed gameplay, classic and advanced horror mechanics, artificial intelligence, and much more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealengine5_endlessrunner"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealengine5_endlessrunner" href="https://youtu.be/tU8npUgUEJU"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 - Endless Runner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/14f477a917db83787abb79a4486e1afee0165c01.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4473bf10b7ee1e48bad933a8c1b2e665"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Develop an Endless Runner game to get familiar with the interface and game development process while learning how to use Unreal Engine 5. Even if an endless runner game isn't your interest, this course provides the steps necessary to create a video game from start to finish. Explore fundamental concepts about game-making and utilize that knowledge in your future projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completecplusplusdevelopercourse"&gt;&lt;a id="completecplusplusdevelopercourse" href="https://youtu.be/U2GVRWcQ9fM"&gt;The Complete C++ Developer Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course will provide you with practical experience in C++. You will learn the basics and advanced concepts of C++, such as data types, arrays, functions, encapsulation, inheritance, exception handling, object-oriented programming (OOP), data structures and a lot more, by developing interesting real-world applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="substancepaintertounrealengine5masterclass"&gt;&lt;a id="substancepaintertounrealengine5masterclass" href="https://youtu.be/ALSfZfgzo2g"&gt;Substance Painter to Unreal Engine 5 Masterclass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/900a20e16fb1d20840f989af8bdb6e900b6636c0.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9252703414b33288da7c4d89a6f79e1f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course will help you in creating an intricate stylized wagon showcased within a campfire scene that breathes life through design and animation. This course will help you learn all the techniques pros use and the process of implementing these techniques in your projects Unreal Engine integration will also be a central part of this course’s learning objectives.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealengine5beginnersguidetobuildinga3denvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealengine5beginnersguidetobuildinga3denvironment" href="https://youtu.be/7yAr3nS2ZWg"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 Beginner's Guide to Building a 3D Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Be enthralled in a full guide to building a game environment in UE5, from creating a landscape to making water flow through your mountains, and learn the best way to place environmental details with this course for beginners.nnWe will go over the entire Quixel library and add realistic elements using the Niagara particle system to build our 3D environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="practicalcplusplus_learncplusplusbasicsstepbystep"&gt;&lt;a id="practicalcplusplus_learncplusplusbasicsstepbystep" href="https://youtu.be/sbnEKncOaHE"&gt;Practical C++: Learn C++ Basics Step by Step&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3230ffef42e905cf90fc46267453f35eef794b30.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=627f269e0049106f8edf210edb1585fb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn to code in C++, one of the oldest and most popular programming languages in the market.nnThis course is created to quickly give you the knowledge and practice you really need to master C++ basics. We will cover core concepts such as variables, arrays, vectors, functions, scope, namespaces, loops, references, prototypes, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cpluspluscrashcourse_quickandpracticallearning"&gt;&lt;a id="cpluspluscrashcourse_quickandpracticallearning" href="https://youtu.be/fIX38_DVgo4"&gt;C++ Crash Course - Quick and Practical Learning&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're a beginner or refreshing your skills, this structured course provides the knowledge needed for software development and technical interviews.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fundamentalsofobject-orientedprogramming_cplusplus"&gt;&lt;a id="fundamentalsofobject-orientedprogramming_cplusplus" href="https://youtu.be/HGHa1TObz8U"&gt;Fundamentals of Object-Oriented Programming - C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The course is designed to provide complete knowledge of object-oriented programming using C++. We will discuss some core OOP concepts such as classes, objects, functions, encapsulation, and polymorphism. Along with learning how to design implement classes, we will cover the best practices for writing and maintaining code&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="buildingmedievalworlds_unrealengine5modularkitbash"&gt;&lt;a id="buildingmedievalworlds_unrealengine5modularkitbash" href="https://youtu.be/EKLuhJUx9qY"&gt;Building Medieval Worlds - Unreal Engine 5 Modular Kitbash&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the power of modular kitbashing and bring your medieval fantasy world to life with UE5. Learn unique techniques for stylized structures, functional water systems, open-world landscapes, custom prop collections, large-scale structures, and more. Build a stunning environment that blurs the line between reality and imagination using 250 modular assets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="creatingstunningenvironmentsinunrealengine5_agameartistbootcamp"&gt;&lt;a id="creatingstunningenvironmentsinunrealengine5_agameartistbootcamp" href="https://youtu.be/Stgdy8BTeio"&gt;Creating Stunning Environments in Unreal Engine 5 - A Game Artist Bootcamp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this practical and comprehensive course, you will learn the art of creating stunning game environments using Unreal Engine 5. From mastering advanced tools and techniques to unleashing your creativity, this course will empower you to build immersive worlds that transport players to breathtaking virtual realms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="completemoderncpluspluscplusplus11and14and17"&gt;&lt;a id="completemoderncpluspluscplusplus11and14and17" href="https://youtu.be/fUzH_sqr7-w"&gt;Complete Modern C++ (C++11/14/17)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course teaches you all the concepts in C++ with the help of examples and aims to make you a proficient C++ developer. You will learn everything from the basics of object-oriented programming to more advanced concepts such as templates and library components.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="behavioraldesignpatternsincplusplus"&gt;&lt;a id="behavioraldesignpatternsincplusplus" href="https://youtu.be/L7ZPg1Ezfmo"&gt;Behavioral Design Patterns in C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This Design Patterns course is a unique offering that focuses on modern C++ features and behavioral design patterns. The course content is extensive and carefully curated, with a deep dive into each pattern to ensure a thorough understanding of its implementation.nnGain a comprehensive understanding of the pattern’s intricacies.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealengine5_thecompletebeginnerscourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealengine5_thecompletebeginnerscourse" href="https://youtu.be/8A1nRh0asME"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 - The Complete Beginner's Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7cd3c8505b4c18fb6f850dddc9cfd40801e2eee9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=105672ac9f6ae849954143eefd7f8d20"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master Unreal Engine 5 with this step-by-step course! Learn to create interactive worlds, use Blueprints for programming, design levels, and package your own games. Perfect for aspiring developers and hobbyists, this course gives you the skills to bring your game ideas to life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealengine5_theintermediatecourse"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealengine5_theintermediatecourse" href="https://youtu.be/LI8O7geC4_k"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 - The Intermediate Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Elevate your game design journey with "Unreal Engine 5: The Intermediate Course." Dive into detailed studies of Materials and Textures, Landscapes and Open Worlds, Skeletal Meshes and Animations, and advanced Blueprint techniques. Transform your basic knowledge into professional-level expertise in Unreal Engine 5.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="unrealengine5forgames_physics"&gt;&lt;a id="unrealengine5forgames_physics" href="https://youtu.be/YHRC0VWV6HQ"&gt;Unreal Engine 5 for Games - Physics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course walks you through Unreal Engine 5’s powerful physics system, starting with the basics of physics bodies, collision volumes, and vectors.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="structuraldesignpatternsinmoderncplusplus"&gt;&lt;a id="structuraldesignpatternsinmoderncplusplus" href="https://youtu.be/h7le9C2srD0"&gt;Structural Design Patterns in Modern C++&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/82c9d096bc903ea6500da966459271155fc8aab6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=102ce69fd39a17898bc9750f12c4c23f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Discover the power of modern C++ design patterns, including adapter, façade, and composite. This course provides a comprehensive understanding of each pattern, complete with real-world examples to help you confidently implement them in your projects and build efficient, scalable software like a pro.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cplusplus20mastery_pureandunfiltered"&gt;&lt;a id="cplusplus20mastery_pureandunfiltered" href="https://youtu.be/80bv6-RPqIE"&gt;C++ 20 Mastery - Pure and Unfiltered&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Delve into the most impactful changes in C++20 in this expertly designed course. From core language upgrades to advanced concepts like coroutines and ranges, gain the knowledge needed to build efficient and scalable C++ applications. Perfect for developers seeking to master modern C++.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
