rybarrierspack"&gt;&lt;a id="militarybarrierspack"&gt;Military Barriers Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/5f44f482311eee0d5279fa8780412c954d33a999.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f599998b4e5c79d66615536372d9952f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Military Barriers Pack with 28 Unique Meshes. This pack includes all showcased assets, high-quality assets with a good level of detail, and assets optimized for game-ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;28 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All Building Assets are Modular&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;128&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 2048, 1024, 128&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Automatically Generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 3 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 28 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 19&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 46&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="suv02driveable"&gt;&lt;a id="suv02driveable" href="https://youtu.be/LfkldymQb3o"&gt;SUV 02 Driveable&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;SUV Driveable / Animated / Realistic / Customizable, AAA Quality, Fully Customizable with separate Parts / Blueprints / Material Instances. There are Roughness / Metallic / Color parameters in material instances so that you can arrange materials easily; the vehicle will be in one blueprint and also eight separate meshes, so you will be able to use it as you wish to, an excellent prop for your Levels / Games and Automotive presentations / ArchViz,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can Activate ( Open / Close ) Car doors with four buttons ( one button for each, Q E R F ) via keyboard, and you can change the camera view while driving the Car.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged , Driveable , Playable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Automotive Industry / ArchViz / Games&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Dirt / Edge Wears&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Lights&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy switch between material values ( roughness / metallic / color )&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One button Animating Car's Doors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 8&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.19 , 4.20 , 4.21 , 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26+, 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxwinter"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxwinter"&gt;SFX Winter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a01bbfb3ebb7e6ace59f870934675614b923fecd.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4fa2a9ea6d35a7afac726094bf471a50"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Immerse your game in a chilling winter atmosphere with this versatile sound pack. From the crunch of footsteps on fresh snow to the cozy murmur of interior winter ambience, this collection is ideal for survival games, winter exploration, and holiday-themed experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Snow walk, run, jump, and land effects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Winter interior ambient loops&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Designed for seamless layering and immersion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect For:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Survival games, winter levels, Christmas events, exploration games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxdustunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxdustunrealengine"&gt;VFX Dust (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d57db8e66a2c0983120d7f787cf94ed28bc1b3ee.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=558ca8c6b2a2a9a858e174136d6a8952"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leartes Presents Awesome VFX Pack:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Dust Sound Effect Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="substance3dpainter_acompleteguideforbeginners"&gt;&lt;a id="substance3dpainter_acompleteguideforbeginners"&gt;Substance 3D Painter: A Complete Guide for Beginners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fa162e418ae54b60fe3e3fb91efd8e273f06ee2d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=baef251a4192b1f547f38e76a2b11fa5"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the world of Unreal Engine 5 as you paint three different types of props in Substance 3D Painter. Our Udemy course is your ticket to mastering the texturing. Led by the seasoned industry professional, Bagher Bolouri, this course is tailored for both beginners and experienced artists. You’ll start by gaining a solid foundation in the principles of modelling, texturing and level art, learning how to execute your vision. Throughout the course, you’ll engage in three different practical projects designed to sharpen your skills and deepen your understanding of the creative process. One will be a complex chair, another will be denim pants and the last one will be a gun. By the end, you’ll emerge with a portfolio-worthy environment, ready to showcase your talent and impress potential employers. Key topics include: Establishing a preliminary spatial design by creating a reference board and a 3D blockout Understanding the principles of PBR texturing and materials Preparing high and low poly models and exporting in Maya Navigating Substance 3D Painter's robust toolset and features Creating materials for soft surfaces, hard surfaces and cloth. Exporting texture sets and rendering the end product in Blender Whether you’re an enthusiast looking to break into the gaming industry or a professional seeking to refine your craft, this course offers invaluable insights and practical skills to elevate your texture and material skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfx3policestationsfx"&gt;&lt;a id="sfx3policestationsfx"&gt;SFX 3 Police Station (SFX)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/b77a874446dad97a91e079d97a4feff62b3f7fdb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0b11fd34e07edafc9a0ad0a899094466"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Retro Police station-themed Sound Pack.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;3 Retro Police Car Sound is available for now. We will add more content soon .&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;1 Ambience Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;1 Typewriter Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;1 Swinging Lamp Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;3 Smoking Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;4 PoliceRadio Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;3 Fluorescent Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;3 Fan Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2 ClockTicking Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2 BurningSmoking Loop Sound&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Total 20 different Sound available in mp3 and WAW format&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="modelingtutorial"&gt;&lt;a id="modelingtutorial"&gt;Modeling Tutorial&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/c3dd07c1918f02a6a5b5af5e3021f361e256bf32.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6021c20c3176ecd6c652fb55ae2438f7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maya+ Zbrush + Substance Painter low poly to high poly workflow Game-Ready Tutorial.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The tutorial subjects are:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ol&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gameready Ornamented Prop Modeling Tutorial in Maya (1 Hour 39 min )&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gameready Ornamented Prop Sculpting Tutorial in Maya (1 Hour 55 min )&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gameready Ornamented Prop Texturing _ Rendering (1 Hour 59 min )&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gameready Ornamented Prop UV Mapping Tutorial in Maya (1 Hour 50 min )&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ol&gt; &lt;p&gt;This Tutorial Series Explains the Game-ready Sculpted prop creating process.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="postapocalypticmeleeweapons_vol2unrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="postapocalypticmeleeweapons_vol2unrealengine"&gt;Post Apocalyptic Melee Weapons VOL.2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a147cc972dd0c6dc255463ad3c03cee195f42aa9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e7020d8831333764cc9e5b12040fae2a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA quality visuals, style, and budget.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;5 Meshes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;High quality and fidelity texture sets - 4k textures&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control the majority of all props and models&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Channel packed Roughness | Metalness | Ambient Occlusion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Realistic Post Process and Look Up Table&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized for games!&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models from all sides&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;High fidelity for use as First Person Weapons (FPS)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;4096 [15]&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2048 [2]&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;1024 [2]&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;512 [1]&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;256 [1]&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;128 [3]&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Scaled to Epic skeleton: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated and per-poly mix based on complexity of asset&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vertex Count: 39452 Tris for all assets combined (See documentation for individual polycounts)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: Small Prop Unreal Generated LODS&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 5&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances:11&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 25&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Windows&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Window/Mac/PS4/Xbox&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="materialassignmenttoolunrealenginetoolplugin"&gt;&lt;a id="materialassignmenttoolunrealenginetoolplugin" href="https://youtu.be/gZCcOSubK-g"&gt;Material Assignment Tool (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3c5bd66a0c20f2fc9f37df79a22a7dffcb5e979b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0aaee7a82b4339c148f94121f5017930"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities. As a Leading Art Outsource company, Leartes Studios is dedicated to pushing the boundaries . The Material Assignment tool makes it easy to track static mesh assets with common slots and allows you to bulk assign materials to them all at once.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As an art outsource company, our primary focus has been on delivering exceptional visual assets, animations, and art production services to game developers. However, recognizing the evolving needs of the industry and the importance of efficient workflows, we have embarked on the development of our groundbreaking code plugin tool.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Important note : Editor Scripting Utilities needs to be enabled.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This Tool is also available in Ultimate Level Art Tool&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quick access to the tool interface with a custom tool menu&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The customizable window for personal uses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiple material assignments for equivalent static mesh actors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;No custom class dependencies can be removed from the project at any time&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Code Modules MaterialAssignment(Editor)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Material Assignment Manager(Editor)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number Of C++ Classes: 6&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 2&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated: No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development: Platforms Win64&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build: Platforms Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="policecharacterandnpcunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="policecharacterandnpcunrealengine"&gt;Police Character / NPC (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/82e4a935ce3b18978512f37b1e723151acc75b1c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=dfe2cd83103f887b436f725e51eac570"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Police Character / NPC / High Quality / Fully Rigged / Ready for Mannequin Animations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The character is made according to Unreal Engine Mannequin Skeleton, and animations will work with it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rigged&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Good to use in Games / Virtual Productions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Customizable Clothes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4096 / 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 12&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 18&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 58&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="1950sbusinessmanandmafiacharacterandnpcandrigged"&gt;&lt;a id="1950sbusinessmanandmafiacharacterandnpcandrigged"&gt;1950s Mafia Character / NPC / Rigged&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/50ae8675c6736b4f2491ec6a24606c09331c052d.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=43f4dba044af7a2143c707f501ba0b14"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;1950s Mafia Character / NPC / High Quality / Fully Rigged / Ready for Mannequin Animations.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Character is made according to Unreal Engine Mannequin Skeleton and all ready animations will work with it.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical Details -&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rigged&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Good to use in Games / Virtual Productions&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Customizable Clothes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully Customizable / Material Variations&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;4096 / 2048&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 12&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 16&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 42&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Unreal Engine Versions: 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , UE5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkhologramsandneonsetsetof33holograms"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkhologramsandneonsetsetof33holograms" href="https://youtu.be/ynMB9wfClnw"&gt;Cyberpunk Holograms / Neon Set ( Set of 33 Holograms )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d4432bc5ebfd8f2cb33ef348c8e5f336114826b6.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=8ad6cb9efec24c5415579fac7c3d8803"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Holograms / Neon Set ( Set of 33 Holograms ) . The set includes 33 different Cyberpunk Holograms. Concept Arts makes all Holograms from the Leartes Team. Holograms have tileable Materials, so you can easily adjust their Material Parameters, colors, Tiles, Emissions, and many more parameters. Excellent pack for your Cyberpunk / Sci-Fi / Futuristic Environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunkstreetlightsunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunkstreetlightsunrealengine"&gt;Cyberpunk Street Lights (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2cf23d019a7cba5a2179e1b4cfef68823c699503.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=12948eb1f88a08e53048c8bbbdbffbc0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Street Lights with 29 Unique Meshes. This pack includes all showcased assets, high-quality assets with a good level of detail, and assets optimized for Game-Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;29 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;512&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;128&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Automatically Generated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 29 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 42&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 50&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.26 , 4.27+ , 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="driveableandanimatedretrocyberpunkhovercar02unrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="driveableandanimatedretrocyberpunkhovercar02unrealengine" href="https://youtu.be/HA4EMd6_DZ0"&gt;Driveable / Animated Retro Cyberpunk Hover Car 02&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Driveable / Animated Retro Cyberpunk Hover Car with customizable materials, you can adjust color/dirt in Material Instance parameters, drive the car in your game level, and fly with the car through your scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; With Custom Cyberpunk Interior&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Driveable / Animated&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Adjustable Materials&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Blueprint Prefab&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 9&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 9&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints : 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 44&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 2048&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="miamiclubmegapack"&gt;&lt;a id="miamiclubmegapack" href="https://youtu.be/GDnDPaCz6gw"&gt;Miami Club Megapack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Miami Club Megapack Environment with 784 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here are our seven months of hard work as the Leartes Team—the Miami Club Megapack UE Environment with over 784 unique meshes, a variety of Blueprints for easy use, and merged assets for optimized performance. We’ve focused on creating a high-quality, immersive nightclub experience while ensuring smooth performance, even with the detailed assets and lighting effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With high-quality textures, dynamic lighting, and interactive elements, the Miami Club Megapack captures the energy of a luxury nightclub. Featuring VIP lounges, dance floors, and vibrant bars, it’s designed for immersive storytelling and optimized for top performance in Unreal Engine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;784 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: No, Nanite Enabled&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 784 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 421&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 1038&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ancientcathedralenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="ancientcathedralenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/4fJh4ClREIE"&gt;Ancient Cathedral Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ancient Cathedral Environment with 141 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;141 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Complex vertex paint setup with multiple lay