al Instances: 198&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 439&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.3, 5.4+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="piratetavernenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="piratetavernenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/_Oq5b9Z-OFo"&gt;Pirate Tavern Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Pirate Tavern, created from an old shipwreck, you can embark on a journey to the magical times of pirates. With high-resolution textures, pirate props, and modular tavern elements, you can build your own custom tavern.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;250 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 3 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 250 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 121&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 171&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5,2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="chinesealleyenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="chinesealleyenvironment" href="https://youtu.be/egtyt-mwI84"&gt;Chinese Alley Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the Chinese Alley project, you can access high-quality meshes and textures designed for your Asian-themed project, including elements like rain and sparks among the ruins. This allows you to create your own chaotic Chinese environments while benefiting from dynamic effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;172 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 172 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 187&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 354&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.3, 5.4, 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultimatelevelarttool"&gt;&lt;a id="ultimatelevelarttool" href="https://youtu.be/HR2Fw-vMwek"&gt;Ultimate Level Art Tool - ULAT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/69a40f17710006d72bf4d952f3f0b117013b29fb.png?auto=compress,format&amp;s=6fbe3bb2b0bdd50b18fa6a2c24a3e4f5"&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities. Leartes Studios is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of being a leading art outsourcing company.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;As an art outsourcing company, our primary focus has been delivering exceptional visual assets, animations, and art production services to game developers. However, recognizing the industry's evolving needs and the importance of efficient workflows, we have embarked on the development of our groundbreaking code plugin tool.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Under the hood, the Ultimate Level Art Tool has an impressive number of features. We are also planning to develop the tool further, expanding its functionality and versatility.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Ultimate Level Art Tool has a lot of features :&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create a fully Modular Building with one tool&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create your custom mesh palette&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Adjustable mesh snapping Modes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;One-click material assigned to the collection&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;One-click create a blueprint from the collection&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;One-click Prop Duplication&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Place multiple modular meshes simultaneously&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create a realistic simulated mesh groups&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Technical details&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quick access to the tool interface with a custom tool menu&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quick workspace setup with drag-and-drop static mesh assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The customizable window for personal uses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiple modular placements simultaneously&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Separate categories for modular and prop placement&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiple material assignments for equivalent static mesh actors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Flexibility to work on multiple structures simultaneously with the collection feature&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;No custom class dependencies can be removed from the project at any time&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Code Modules UltimateLevelArtTool(Editor)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Number Of C++ Classes 75&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints - 23&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated - No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms - Win64&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms - Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="rallypointenvironmentsci-fiandfuturisticandmodularunity"&gt;&lt;a id="rallypointenvironmentsci-fiandfuturisticandmodularunity" href="https://youtu.be/JazWcwMAU0Y"&gt;The Rally Point Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Rally Point Environment by Guillaume Hecht is a Gears of War-inspired Environment with 257 Meshes , 13 Decals , 27 Blueprints for easy use, and 183 Materials / Material Instances . Former Ubisoft created the environment, which is currently called Cloud Chamber. Employee talented Environment Artist Guillaume Hecht. It is a high-quality environment with many assets and materials, including levels. The building meshes are modular and fit in a 50cm grid. It is a great package to create or populate your game levels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality / Big Pack&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Over 250 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;13 Decals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A lot of HQ Props&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Example Map / Overview Map&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 257&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes up to 4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 183&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints : 27&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 423&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1K , 2K&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Engine Versions : 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , UE5 , 5.1 , 5.2 , 5.3 , 5.4 , 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="japanesetemple"&gt;&lt;a id="japanesetemple" href="https://youtu.be/SVtgD_o4gBc"&gt;Japanese Temple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Imagine a Japanese temple with a massive wooden structure. Inside the temple, you will feel small. The project includes many ready-to-use braziers, candles, and sculptures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Japanese Temple Environment with 140+ Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;148 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Detail&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 3 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 148 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 146&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 147&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5,2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="feudaljapanwarroom"&gt;&lt;a id="feudaljapanwarroom" href="https://youtu.be/27anFQ41_sE"&gt;Feudal Japan Warroom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;All Assets have great details, including sculpted meshes, weapons, sculptures, etc. This pack will significantly add to your Medieval / Feudal Japanese Levels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: (Please include a full, comprehensive list of the features of the product)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;High Quality&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unique Concepts For Assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 30&lt;/p&g