cclusion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Realistic Post Process and Look Up Table&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized for FPS games!&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Pivots placed for ease of animation and usage&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes: 4096 [15], 1024 [2], 512 [1], 256 [1], 128 [3]&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Scaled to Epic Skeleton: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, automatically generated and per-poly mix based on complexity of asset&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Vertex Count:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Acton (5276 Tris)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Cedarville (9584 Tris)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Espena (6525 Tris)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Jailmen (12047 Tris)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;McKennan (8673 Tris)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: Base LOD&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 45&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 8&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 23&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Windows&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Window/Mac/PS4/Xbox&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stableenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="stableenvironmentunrealengine"&gt;Stable Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/17813e0f6dc8a55781b6ccbcf12979d06d9c5e54.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=50d4222b0260a726075d61a47fa8f536"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stable Environment with 33 Unique Meshes. Awesome Environment Pack for Medieval / Western Set-Ups. You will get an example Scene inside the pack. You can use this pack to create a Scene with it or populate your Scenes with Its Meshes.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features :&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / High Quality&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Complete Environment Set&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes: 2048,1024,512&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 3 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 33 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 33&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 49&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 4.25+ , UE5 , 5.1 , 5.2 , 5.3 , 5.4 , 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
