lt;a href="#bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#modularcastleanddungeon_naturemanufacture"&gt;Modular Castle &amp; Dungeon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#fishnetpro_networkingevolved"&gt;FishNet Pro: Networking Evolved&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bloodeffectspack"&gt;Blood Effects Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mystifyfx"&gt;Mystify FX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sci-fiarsenal"&gt;Sci-Fi Arsenal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#smoothsync"&gt;Smooth Sync&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#horrorprison"&gt;Horror Prison&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#horrormultiplayergametemplate"&gt;Horror Multiplayer Game Template&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#6000fantasyicons_unity"&gt;6000 Fantasy Icons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#kaykit_dungeonremasteredpackforunity"&gt;KayKit - Dungeon Remastered Pack (for Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#volfx_vfxtoolkit"&gt;VolFx - VFX Toolkit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#intrigues_unity"&gt;Intrigues&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cartoonfx4remaster"&gt;Cartoon FX 4 Remaster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#wireframeshader"&gt;Wireframe Shader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#everydaymotionpack"&gt;Everyday Motion Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#drawxxl"&gt;Draw XXL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#sci-fibosspack"&gt;Sci-Fi Boss pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#battleships2"&gt;Battleships 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#3dfish"&gt;3D Fish&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="lowpolytreespack_lmhpoly"&gt;&lt;a id="lowpolytreespack_lmhpoly" href="https://youtu.be/lGkfcSS4nsA"&gt;Low Poly Trees - Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;1170 game-ready low poly tree assets optimized for low-end PC, console, VR, and mobile devices. Just drag and drop to your scene to achieve beautiful results in no time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;PACKAGE CONTAINS 446 unique low poly tree prefabs in different types + the same 446 tree prefabs with snow. 114 unique low poly wood prefabs like stumps, logs, and firewood + the same 114 wood prefabs with snow. 12 other prefabs like palm leaves, pine spikes, apples, and coconuts + the same 12 prefabs with snow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also, you get 26 BONUS prefabs like tileable terrain &amp;amp; water planes, hills, mountains, clouds, and 3 simple scripts for the camera, sun, and cloud control.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;FEATURES LODs Optimized colliders. Lightmap baking support. Real-world scale. Easy to change colors. Easy to use. Detailed documentation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="lightingbox2next-genlightingsolution"&gt;&lt;a id="lightingbox2next-genlightingsolution" href="https://youtu.be/b7s-LddLPuo"&gt;Lighting Box 2 Next-Gen Lighting Solution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a real time saver solution to get AAA looking lighting in a few seconds or minutes even without any lighting experience&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cyberpunk_cybercityhdrpplusbip"&gt;&lt;a id="cyberpunk_cybercityhdrpplusbip" href="https://youtu.be/Y_FJH5BMrtY"&gt;cyberpunk - Cyber City (HDRP + BIP)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bundle includes full modular pack for creating high detailed realistic cyberpunk city, streets, alleys, city blocks etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Includes: walls, windows, doors, props, wires, lights, neons, advertisements, cars, robots... etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also contains 3d physics based route system for robots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can create realistic city, sci-fi, modern-retro, vintage, fantasy, retro cyberpunk, XXI century-light - 'any colour you like'.' Note: Human example models not included.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt20"&gt;Pay $20 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="dragons_fantasyrpg_customizabledragonpack"&gt;&lt;a id="dragons_fantasyrpg_customizabledragonpack" href="https://youtu.be/xmPtR20uPUc"&gt;Dragons - Fantasy RPG - Customizable Dragon Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;AAA quality modular dragons! 3 Heads, 2 Tails, Mesh Morphing, and more. These animated dragons are among the most popular on the Asset Store and look amazing in games.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Customize the dragons with multiple body parts, saddle parts, and mesh morphing to achieve unique looks among hordes of bad guys.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="5000fantasyicons"&gt;&lt;a id="5000fantasyicons" href="https://youtu.be/9aHqdbHy7OQ"&gt;5000 Fantasy Icons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A large set of icons in fantasy style. Here you will find all types of icons, as the package includes: skill, item, profession, weapon and armor icons. All icons are hand-drawn in the same style, it is also well-combined with both classic and flat-style interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="advancedfoliagepack"&gt;&lt;a id="advancedfoliagepack" href="https://youtu.be/SvGeuVnCBNQ"&gt;Advanced Foliage Pack 2.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Group of foliage, grass, flowers, roots, trunk models, and ground textures. Asset data were scanned and carefully optimized. Shaders for foliage, rocks, and trunks support dynamic snow cover.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Content: • 29 ground texture sets; • 10 grass atlas sets; • 20 Unity grass billboards; • 26 Unity grass optimized • 2 scanned, optimised trunks with snow version; • 6 root models with snow version; • In ground textures you will find: needles, litter, sand, road, dirt, mud, moss, roots, rocks, leaves, grass, pebbles, stones, snow • Built-in, URP, and HD RP support; • 6 grass shaders (lite, standard specular with snow variants); • 4 standard shaders with snow support; • SRP batcher and DOTS instancing support for HD and URP • All shaders have a snow support version."&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="toonsuburbanpack"&gt;&lt;a id="toonsuburbanpack" href="https://youtu.be/jojh_RKXqAM"&gt;Toon Suburban Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kick-start your level building with this stylized urban environment:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Over 800 prefabs, ranging from modular buildings and interior assets, to vehicles, road systems and characters.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• Modular assets for building your own houses, interiors, shops and much more.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• Over 70 pre-made building and interior presets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• Vehicles with interiors and openable doors, trunks and detachable wheels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• Customizable characters and pre-made presets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• A large showcase scene incorporating all the assets from the package.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="speechrecognitionsystem"&gt;&lt;a id="speechrecognitionsystem" href="https://youtu.be/zAqZnnuGh88"&gt;Speech Recognition System&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Real-time voice recognition system.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: • Does not require Internet connection; • High quality and speed of speech recognition; • Supports 24 different languages; • Possibility to work with Oculus Quest; • Multiplatformity (Windows, iOS, Android, macOS, Linux); • Easiness of integration.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="modularcastleanddungeon_naturemanufacture"&gt;&lt;a id="modularcastleanddungeon_naturemanufacture" href="https://youtu.be/Rvbb4PruPZo"&gt;Modular Castle &amp; Dungeon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Over 1000 models in 1300 prefabs will help you to build castles, dungeons, towns, towers, temples, bridges, and walls. The pack contains modular content from small elements like ornaments up to big objects like whole towers. A complex demo scene 1x1 km with indoor and outdoor locations shows you all the options and power of the pack. Advanced fast shaders allow you to vertex paint, heat, glow, make objects wet, or even top/snow cover your objects to customize them even more. A detailed tutorial connected with the asset will help you use all the pack's features.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="fishnetpro_networkingevolved"&gt;&lt;a id="fishnetpro_networkingevolved" href="https://youtu.be/yM5dBko9SOs"&gt;FishNet Pro: Networking Evolved&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fish-Networking (FishNet) is a powerful, open-source Unity networking library built for modern multiplayer games. It offers high performance, flexible server-authoritative architecture, and out-of-the-box features like prediction, lag compensation, scene management, and networked physics. Designed with scalability and ease of use in mind, FishNet supports both client-hosted and dedicated server models. Whether you're building fast-paced action games or large online worlds, FishNet gives you the tools and control needed to create smooth, secure, and responsive multiplayer experiences.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bloodeffectspack"&gt;&lt;a id="bloodeffectspack" href="https://youtu.be/xq0S7WOggXs"&gt;Blood Effects Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Deliver intense gore and visceral impact with this high-quality blood effects pack for Unity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Compatible with Built-in RP, URP, and HDRP (URP/HDRP shaders created via Shader Graph), it includes lightweight, PBR-based, mobile-friendly assets optimized for real-time performance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Packed with blood splashes, decals, projectors, gut effects, and UI screen overlays, each prefab is ready to drag-and-drop into your scenes with minimal setup. Perfect for horror, action, or stylized games that demand fast, dramatic visual feedback and a polished look — across desktop, console, and mobile platforms, including Unity 6.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="mystifyfx"&gt;&lt;a id="mystifyfx" href="https://youtu.be/aSthuf1XN-o"&gt;Mystify FX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mystify FX offers a robust collection of high-performance shaders dedicated to distortion, refraction, and blending. Achieve a wide spectrum of stylized visual effects, from subtle heat haze and liquid-like surfaces to dynamic warping and seamless layer blending. Each shader is highly customizable, providing granular control over parameters to fine-tune the look and feel of your effects. Optimized for performance, Mystify FX allows you to enhance your project's aesthetic without sacrificing frame rate. Whether you're aiming for subtle environmental enhancements or dramatic visual transformations, Mystify FX provides the versatility and power you need to bring your artistic vision to fruition effortlessly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sci-fiarsenal"&gt;&lt;a id="sci-fiarsenal" href="https://youtu.be/ZSmezg0q1eI"&gt;Sci-Fi Arsenal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Created for Unity's Built-in Render Pipeline, with an upgrade package included for the Universal Render Pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This vibrant collection of particle effects is built to light up sci-fi battles and bring energy to your worlds—whether you're crafting a action filled shooter, a tense RPG, or a fast-paced platformer.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The pack features 92 unique effects and over 580 prefabs, organized into intuitive categories and offered in multiple color variations to suit a wide range of styles. From missiles and flamethrowers to explosions and impact bursts, each effect is designed to be responsive, eye-catching, and easy to drag &amp;amp; drop or instantiate into any project scene.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With additive textures that deliver a glowing look without the need for post-processing, these FX are ideal for both 2D and 3D games. A demo project is included to help you preview and test everything right away. Simply import the asset (and upgrade to Universal if needed), add the scenes to build settings and press play in any scene to browse the effects freely.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="smoothsync"&gt;&lt;a id="smoothsync" href="https://youtu.be/Y1XvMnuJRqE"&gt;Smooth Sync&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Smooths Rigidbodies and Transforms over the network with ease. Just add the SmoothSync script to any game object and watch it be smoooooth.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Simple drop-in setup for Netcode for GameObjects, Mirror, PUN, PUN2, MLAPI, FishNet, and UNet. No coding required!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We aimed to improve NetworkTransform on all fronts. Smooth Sync is more configurable, uses less bandwidth, and gives you smoother and more accurate syncing of your objects. We only send what you need, reducing the networking costs over Unity's Network Transform by up to 60%.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ideal for syncing anything that moves. Vehicles, character controllers, even objects controlled by physics. Works great even at low send rates.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Used by over 1 million gamers!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="horrorprison"&gt;&lt;a id="horrorprison" href="https://youtu.be/mcekvFUOi4k"&gt;Horror Prison&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Horror Prison is a modular interior environment of an isolated island prison where secret experiments went horribly wrong. The asset includes only indoor corridors and rooms (no exterior), and supports HDRP, URP, and Built-in pipelines. Designed for PC projects and VR with scene optimization. Perfect for horror games focused on isolation and unease.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="horrormultiplayergametemplate"&gt;&lt;a id="horrormultiplayergametemplate" href="https://youtu.be/6WudzF2M-Tw"&gt;Horror Multiplayer Game Template&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Create AAA-quality multiplayer horror games with this feature-rich, production-ready template. Players take on the role of survivors trying to escape, or killers hunting them down. Packed with essential systems, it delivers the core mechanics that power polished and immersive horror experiences. Add and customize characters, abilities, maps, and items using modular components built for scalability and speed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="6000fantasyicons_unity"&gt;&lt;a id="6000fantasyicons_unity" href="https://youtu.be/xXEtS3Tktv4"&gt;6000 Fantasy Icons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A large set of icons in fantasy style. Here you will find all types of icons, as the package includes: skill, item, profession, weapon, armor, building and avatar icons. All icons are hand-drawn in the same style, it is also well-combined with both classic and flat-style interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="kaykit_dungeonremasteredpackforunity"&gt;&lt;a id="kaykit_dungeonremasteredpackforunity" href="https://youtu.be/U2kUs0_8510"&gt;KayKit - Dungeon Remastered Pack (for Unity)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The KayKit - Dungeon Remastered Asset Pack includes 280+ stylized 3D dungeon assets and props. Build your ideal dungeon with modular floors, walls, stairs, doors, and decorate with chests, barrels, traps, furniture, tavern pieces, a modular bar, beds, and more. All models are low-poly optimized, textured, and suitable for any platform (including mobile). Each asset is carefully crafted to ensure a consistent visual style and easy implementation. A perfect starting point for any gamedev creating a roguelike, dungeon crawler, or top-down RPG!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="volfx_vfxtoolkit"&gt;&lt;a id="volfx_vfxtoolkit" href="https://youtu.be/0Byz2CEw-y8"&gt;VolFx - VFX Toolkit&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;VolFx ☄ – Stylized Unity VFX Toolkit&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;• Give your Unity game a cinematic makeover with VolFx – a modular stylized VFX toolkit that makes every scene feel like art. • Modular Pipeline: Reorder and stack custom post-process passes and shaders for unique visuals • Selective Effects: Apply FX only to chosen objects (e.g. blur a background behind a character) using Unity layer masks • Real-time Control: Tweak effects at runtime via Unity’s Volume profiles and Timeline for dynamic, on-the-fly adjustments • Cinematic Stylization: Includes pre-built stylized FX (impacts, magic, filmic filters, etc.) to add a hand-crafted, game-inspired flair.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;VolFx is lightweight, easy to integrate, and ideal for any project seeking a stylized, cinematic VFX boost.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="intrigues_unity"&gt;&lt;a id="intrigues_unity" href="https://youtu.be/NWCkh63IWrM"&gt;Intrigues&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Intrigues lets you create dynamic families, factions, and branching narratives without writing a single line of code. Designed with a AAA-quality node-based editor, it empowers you to build rich, interactive stories full of secrets, shifting alliances, and emergent drama. Perfect for RPGs, strategy, and simulation games, Intrigues enhances your project with systems that spark curiosity and reward player exploration. All logic is visual, modular, and fully editor-driven — bring your world to life with depth and intrigue.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cartoonfx4remaster"&gt;&lt;a id="cartoonfx4remaster" href="https://youtu.be/cdp6fFemWwY"&gt;Cartoon FX 4 Remaster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cartoon FX 4 Remaster"" is the fourth pack in a series of stylized particle effects for Unity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This one is mainly focused on environmental, space and weapons effect, with 50+ prefabs included along with some variants for them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;They are ready to be used in a project by directly instantiating the prefabs through your scripts, and are easily customizable if your code architecture is more demanding.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;An editor is included to easily change the colors, hues, speed, size, etc. of the effects without needing to go deep into editing the various particle systems that each effect has.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a bonus, a discount is automatically applied for the ""Cartoon FX Remaster Bundle"" on the Unity Asset Store if you own a license of any of the four included packs (thus including this one)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="wireframeshader"&gt;&lt;a id="wireframeshader" href="https://youtu.be/hSQiK1GxSRw"&gt;Wireframe Shader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enhance visual representation of your 3D model by emphasizing the underlying structure, revealing the edges and form in a clear, geometric style. This shader is ideal for creating stylized graphics, analyzing mesh topology, or debugging geometry.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Designed for seamless compatibility across all devices, including mobile, VR, and high-end PCs, this shader maintains consistent visual quality without any compromises.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With one-node integration support for Unity's Shader Graph and Amplify Shader Editor, Wirframe Shader ensures limitless customization possibilities. Developers and artists can craft unique shader effects and variations effortlessly, unlocking unlimited creative potential.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="everydaymotionpack"&gt;&lt;a id="everydaymotionpack" href="https://youtu.be/ZE-oKAFCXj8"&gt;Everyday Motion Pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;EverydayMotionPack is a hand-crafted animation set built for Unity creators who want to add life and realism to their characters through everyday motions. This pack offers a curated selection of socially-driven movements like walking with purpose, standing casually, gesturing during conversation, reacting naturally, and transitioning smoothly between idle states.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Optimized for Unity’s Humanoid rig system, each animation is loop-ready, lightweight, and easy to integrate. The focus isn’t on flashy or exaggerated actions—but on subtle, believable motions that bring out personality in NPCs and main characters alike.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perfect for indie developers and small studios, this pack makes it simple to create immersive social spaces, dialogue-driven scenes, or background character animations in a fraction of the time. Whether you’re building a slice-of-life simulation, a narrative game, or a mobile app with interactive characters, EverydayMotionPack gives you the tools to make your virtual world feel truly alive.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="drawxxl"&gt;&lt;a id="drawxxl" href="https://youtu.be/O1jGSWd9nwQ"&gt;Draw XXL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Draw XXL is an extensive set of visual debugging and development tools. It can be used as components without any code or like debug lines as one-line-calls from anywhere in your code.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you are just looking to increase your options from Unitys limited Debug.DrawLine(), learn some more about the Game Engine by visualizing basics like quaternion and euler rotations or boost your productivity with charts or physics visualization: Draw XXL got it covered.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Works in Edit Mode, Play Mode and in builds. Can draw as gizmo lines, debug lines, handles lines or as mesh. Full C# source code included. Draws shapes, text, game engine basics, charts, physics, measurements, icons, in world space and screen space.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sci-fibosspack"&gt;&lt;a id="sci-fibosspack" href="https://youtu.be/dPXvT4WolOE"&gt;Sci-Fi Boss pack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack contains 7 Animated game-ready characters. The main feature of this pack is carefully crafted animations to make the battles even more exciting.   7 characters, each character have 4-5 skin unique 24-48 animations for each characters&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="battleships2"&gt;&lt;a id="battleships2" href="https://youtu.be/yz_ep8JLOVs"&gt;Battleships 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Battleships 2 by FORGE3D—a premium space ships fleet pack featuring 25 uniquely designed ships, 27 modular turrets, and 13 structures and props. Compatible with Unity's Built-in, URP, and HDRP render pipelines, it offers flexible customization options, including team colors, engine glows, and emissive effects via Amplify Shader Editor. Perfect for prototyping or production, Battleships 2 delivers a polished, ready-to-deploy arsenal for any sci-fi universe.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="3dfish"&gt;&lt;a id="3dfish" href="https://youtu.be/OOzC3r0pBCo"&gt;3D Fish&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;With its clean and stylish low-poly visuals, this asset allows you to quickly and easily create optimized 3D ocean environments for casual games. It features a variety of fish, marine props, and built-in animations, enabling efficient scene construction and expressive game atmospheres.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
